                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18071028-77-off429 t18071028-77-cd430"></join>, three yards of cloth, value 12 s. and two yards of gingham, value 3 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18071028-77-victim794" type="victimName">
                     Benjamin 
                     Markham
